# Tabs — Visual Spec

## CSS classes

- `.acko-tabs` — base wrapper
- `.acko-tabs-list` — flex
- Underline: `.acko-tabs-list-underline`, `.acko-tab-underline`, `.acko-tab-underline-active`
- Pill: `.acko-tabs-list-pill`, `.acko-tab-pill`, `.acko-tab-pill-active`
- Enclosed: `.acko-tab-enclosed`, `.acko-tab-enclosed-active`
- Sizes: `.acko-tab-sm`, `.acko-tab-md`
- `.acko-tab-icon` — scale-16
- `.acko-tab-full-width .acko-tab-*` — flex-1 justify-center
- `.acko-tab-disabled` — opacity, cursor, pointer-events
